<plot>When the stakes are high enough, anything can be justified...even if that means killing your best friend at his own birthday to cover up an elaborate embezzlement scandal. Sound complicated? Don't worry, as the plot gets more tangled the chemistry only heats up as 4 hilarious characters stumble their way through the worst thought-out murder in history. A lack of morals, raw sensuality and first degree homicide collide in this fast-paced black comedy reminiscent of the classic board game "Clue".</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?151475</url></doc>
